<p>
Two adjoining fragments of a <rs type="material">white marble</rs> <rs type="catMonument"><rs type="catMonument">statue base</rs> shaft</rs>, without moulding (together <measure dim="height" type="length">0.46</measure> × <measure dim="width" type="length">1.08</measure> × <measure dim="depth" type="length">0.42</measure>). The upper left corner survives as a separate fragment.</p>
</div>

<div type="description" n="text" part="N" sample="complete" org="uniform">
<head>Description of Text</head>
